The western equatorial region of ["Dya"], an ocean with 5 islands forested with giant ["Shroom"]s and populated by ["Gnome"]s and other magical creatures.  Occia is the home of the BlueShard of HexForce and considered LawfulNice.  The people of Occia organize themselves into communes and have no central government.

 * allied with ["Euia"]
 * opposed to ["Oria"]
 * neighbors ["Euia"], ["Dysia"], ["Borea"], and ["Austra"]
 * politically communist
 * morally ["LawfulNice"]
